  "description": "<i>Seabase Delta</i> is a text adventure with graphics that was developed using the <a href=\"https://www.mobygames.com/search/quick?gamegroup=Quill+%2f+PAW+games\">Quill</a> game writing software package.<br><br>This game is a sequel to the game <a href=\"https://www.mobygames.com/game/subsunk\">Subsunk</a>. The previous game saw the player, in the role of Ed Lions, aboard a submarine that had been sunk by enemy powers. The task there was to send a message back to base requesting help.<br><br>This game picks up from that point. The enemy have intercepted the message and, using a mysterious magnetic force, have taken the submarine to their underwater base. The player, again in the role of Ed Lions, starts the game in a walkway to the base. Beside him is a dead body and a briefcase. Ed must explore the base and find a way to escape.<br><br>\n",
